ressible, homogeneous magnetohydrodynamic\n(MHD) simulation and associate it with previous results. It follows that the\nstronger (weaker) the turbulence, the more (less) complex the magnetic field\nand the stronger (weaker) the reconnection field and thus the ensuing\nreconnection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Mar 2020 06:02:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Apr 2020 18:23:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 8 Apr 2020 21:29:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2020 17:27:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
